title: WEDNESDAY 2/10 - Patrick Mahomes Surgery
itunes:title: WEDNESDAY 2/10 - Patrick Mahomes Surgery
description:
Seahawks quarterback Russell Wilson says he wants to have a say in Seattle roster moves (0:07), while Chiefs quarterback Patrick Mahomes (1:21) set to undergo surgery on his injured foot. Speaking of quarterbacks, you can see the possible top-overall pick Trevor Lawrence in action at his pro day live on NFL Network this Friday (1:54)
